Package common

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IAddUserMessage
    Message type that is sent to other users to inform them to add the user returned by getUser to their group.
    ICommunicate
    This interface provides the ability to communicate with a remote chat room.
    IConnect
    Connection API to allow users to connect with other users and see what groups they are in so that they can join them.
    IGetAlgoCommandMessage
    Message type that should be sent to a user to request an algoCommand corresponding to the class returned by requestedClass.
    ILocalModelAdapter
    This is the adapter between AlgoCommands and the model.
    IRemoveUserMessage
    Message type that should be sent to a user to inform them to remove the user returned by getUser from their group.
    ISendAlgoCommandMessage
    Message type that should be sent to a user to send (an algoCommand for and unknown message type) to a receiver.
